\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7628901 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9765293\charrsid4015401 Your name is Mrs Thompson, what's this address Mrs Thompson?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4598894 FT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9765293\charrsid4015401 131, Hurst Park Drive.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7628901 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9765293\charrsid4015401 And you are a widow aren't you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4598894 FT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9765293\charrsid4015401 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7628901 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9765293\charrsid4015401 When were you }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3963911 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9765293\charrsid4015401 ?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4598894 FT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9765293\charrsid4015401 1912.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7628901 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9765293\charrsid4015401 What year were you born?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4598894 FT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9765293\charrsid4015401 May - oh 1890 I think.1893
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7628901 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9765293\charrsid4015401 And where were you born?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4598894 FT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9765293\charrsid4015401 Well I was born in the Dingle. Toxteth is it. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7628901 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9765293\charrsid4015401 How many years did you live in the house where you were born?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4598894 FT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9765293\charrsid4015401 I can't tell you that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7628901 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9765293\charrsid4015401 You don't know?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4598894 FT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9765293\charrsid4015401 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7628901 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9765293\charrsid4015401 You don't know what house you were born in then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4598894 FT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9765293\charrsid4015401 Well I was born in Upper Mann Street. And christened at the Domestic Mission. In Mill Street.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7628901 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9765293\charrsid4015401 Did you live there 'til the end of 1918?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4598894 FT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9765293\charrsid4015401 Oh no. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7628901 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9765293\charrsid4015401 How many moves did you have?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4598894 FT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9765293\charrsid4015401 Don't ask me that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7628901 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9765293\charrsid4015401 Do you remember one house that stands out in your memory that you may have lived in longer than any other?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4598894 FT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9765293\charrsid4015401 Do you mean - before I was }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3963911 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid9765293\charrsid4015401  or after?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7628901 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9765293\charrsid4015401 Up to 1918 - before you were }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3963911 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid9765293\charrsid4015401  - when you were a kiddie - before you went to school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4598894 FT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9765293\charrsid4015401 Well I think 42 Eck Street. That was - off Dove Street. Yes. Yes, that's right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7628901 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9765293\charrsid4015401 Do you remember why the family made all those moves?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4598894 FT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9765293\charrsid4015401 No, I think when they - they moved from Dingle - the first - the only move I remember is Eden Street, Lodge Lane.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7628901 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9765293\charrsid4015401 And do you know why they moved?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4598894 FT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9765293\charrsid4015401 Well they moved - for a cheaper house and a bigger house, you know, more rooms.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7628901 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9765293\charrsid4015401 How many brothers and sisters did you have?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4598894 FT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9765293\charrsid4015401 Well - four brothers.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7628901 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9765293\charrsid4015401 Who was the eldest of the brothers and when was he born?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4598894 FT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9765293\charrsid4015401 Joseph.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7628901 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9765293\charrsid4015401 Any idea when he was born?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4598894 FT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9765293\charrsid4015401 No. He would be - over the nineties now.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7628901 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9765293\charrsid4015401 Older than you was he?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4598894 FT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9765293\charrsid4015401 Oh yes, the eldest. I've just buried a sister eighty-three.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7628901 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9765293\charrsid4015401 Who was the next brother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4598894 FT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9765293\charrsid4015401 It was a sister - Helen. Margaret Helen.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7628901 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9765293\charrsid4015401 Do you remember when she was born?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4598894 FT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9765293\charrsid4015401 The 19}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \super\insrsid9765293\charrsid4015401 th}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid9765293\charrsid4015401  of October but don't ask me the year. Eighteen months after he was born so - and I don't know when he was born.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7628901 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9765293\charrsid4015401 Eighteen months later?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4598894 FT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9765293\charrsid4015401 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7628901 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9765293\charrsid4015401 Who was born after Helen?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4598894 FT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9765293\charrsid4015401 Sam. Samuel.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7628901 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9765293\charrsid4015401 Do you know when Sam was born - any idea?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4598894 FT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9765293\charrsid4015401 Well they were all pretty much between eighteen months and two years between. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7628901 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9765293\charrsid4015401 Who was born after Sam?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4598894 FT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9765293\charrsid4015401 Elizabeth. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7628901 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9765293\charrsid4015401 And after Elizabeth?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4598894 FT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9765293\charrsid4015401 Harry. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7628901 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9765293\charrsid4015401 And after Harry?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4598894 FT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9765293\charrsid4015401 Fred.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7628901 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9765293\charrsid4015401 Can you remember any of their birthdays at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4598894 FT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9765293\charrsid4015401 I know the dates.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7628901 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9765293\charrsid4015401 But you don't know the actual years?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4598894 FT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9765293\charrsid4015401 Yes - no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7628901 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9765293\charrsid4015401 But you reckon there was about two years between each?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4598894 FT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9765293\charrsid4015401 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7628901 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9765293\charrsid4015401 That's Joe, Helen, Sam, Elisabeth, Harry, Fred.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4598894 FT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9765293\charrsid4015401 Then me - little me.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7628901 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9765293\charrsid4015401 What was your first name?
