\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4598894 FT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9765293\charrsid4015401 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7628901 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9765293\charrsid4015401 Did she belong to a sa}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4854737\charrsid4015401 vings club - a boot club or a s}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9765293\charrsid4015401 ick club, f}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4854737\charrsid4015401 u}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9765293\charrsid4015401 neral club?
