e breakfast after he'd - seen to things in town.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7628901 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9765293\charrsid4015401 He'd come back?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4598894 FT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9765293\charrsid4015401 Yes. No, he wouldn't come back. He'd have it out.
