\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4598894 FT  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9765293\charrsid4015401 No, I don't remember that - no.
